{"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/buswatchname(bustype:name:flags:nameappearedhandler:namevanishedhandler:userdata:userdatafreefunc:)"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Starts watching ","type":"text"},{"code":"name","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" on the bus specified by ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"busType"},{"text":" and calls","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameAppearedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameVanishedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":" when the name is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"known to have an owner respectively known to lose its"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"owner. Callbacks will be invoked in the thread-default main context"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(see [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.MainContext.push_thread_default"},{"type":"text","text":"])"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"of the thread you are calling this function from.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO"]]},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"busWatchName"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"busType"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"GBusType","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@EA@GBusType"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"name"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gchar","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"BusNameWatcherFlags","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO19BusNameWatcherFlagsV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BusNameWatcherFlags"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"nameAppearedHandler"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"GBusNameAppearedCallback","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GBusNameAppearedCallback","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"? = nil, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"nameVanishedHandler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GBusNameVanishedCallback","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GBusNameVanishedCallback"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil, "},{"text":"userData","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil, "},{"text":"userDataFreeFunc","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GDestroyNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@GDestroyNotify"},{"text":"? = nil) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You are guaranteed that one of the handlers will be invoked after"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling this function. When you are done watching the name, just"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"call "},{"code":"g_bus_unwatch_name()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" with the watcher id this function"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"returns."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the name vanishes or appears (for example the application owning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the name could restart), the handlers are also invoked. If the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection"},{"type":"text","text":" that is used for watching the name disconnects, then"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"nameVanishedHandler","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is invoked since it is no longer"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"possible to access the name."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Another guarantee is that invocations of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameAppearedHandler"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and "},{"code":"nameVanishedHandler","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" are guaranteed to alternate; that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"is, if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameAppearedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":" is invoked then you are"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"guaranteed that the next time one of the handlers is invoked, it"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"will be ","type":"text"},{"code":"nameVanishedHandler","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". The reverse is also true."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This behavior makes it very simple to write applications that want","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to take action when a certain ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"dbus-name-watching.html#d-bus-name-watching","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Basically, the application should create object proxies in","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameAppearedHandler"},{"text":" and destroy them again (if any) in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"nameVanishedHandler","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Function","symbolKind":"func","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO12busWatchName0B4Type4name5flags0F15